<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">DAY TRIP TO ARUSHA NATIONAL PARK</h2>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Price start From 360 USD.</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a full-day safari adventure in Arusha National Park, a hidden gem located at the foothills of majestic . Known for its diverse landscapes, beautiful scenery, and unique wildlife, the park offers an excellent safari experience just a short drive from Arusha.</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Explore lush montane forests, open grasslands, sparkling lakes, and the scenic Ngurdoto Crater while searching for wildlife. Arusha National Park is famous for its large populations of giraffes, zebras, buffaloes, warthogs, bushbucks, waterbucks, and the rare black-and-white colobus monkeys. Although predators are less common, the park's rich biodiversity and stunning views make it a rewarding destination for nature lovers.</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">The Momella Lakes attract a variety of birdlife, including flamingos, pelicans, herons, kingfishers, and numerous migratory species, making the park a paradise for bird enthusiasts.</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">A picnic lunch will be served at a scenic site within the park, followed by an afternoon game drive before returning to Arusha.</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Arusha National Park is unique for its spectacular landscapes, abundant birdlife, Mount Meru views, and the opportunity to experience Tanzania's wildlife in a peaceful and uncrowded environment.</p>
<h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Included</h2>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Park entrance fees</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Professional English-speaking safari guide</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Private 4x4 safari vehicle with pop-up roof</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Picnic lunch</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Bottled drinking water</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Government taxes and VAT</p>
<h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Not Included</h2>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• International flights</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Travel insurance</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Personal expenses</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Alcoholic and soft drinks</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Tips and gratuities</p>
<p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">• Items of a personal nature</p>
  </div>
</section>

